Text: What’s the best form of birth control
Message JSON: {"userId":"c8d1de3c-103d-4aae-89dd-f78da63c0173","text":"What’s the best form of birth control"}

Text: Choosing the best birth control is a really personal decision. There are 18 different types to choose from and they each work differently. You have to use a condom every time you have sex, take the pill daily, get a new patch every week, change the ring every month, and the IUD or implant can last for years.
